Thanks a lot! :rolleyes:

[font=arial black]Edit:[/font] Well, I tried…I failed. Haven’t done Eclipse a lot!

Here’s the code part:

} if (playerCommand.startsWith("bounty")) { c.getPA().movePlayer(3179, 3684, 0); } if(playerCommand.startsWith("unpc")) c.isNpc = false; c.updateRequired = true; c.appearanceUpdateRequired = true; }
